Welcome to Simulocean's Documentation
========================================

`Simulocean`_ (click  :download:`me <./_build/latex/simulocean.pdf>` to download user manual) is a web-based
deployment and visualization framework for coastal modeling and beyond.Simulocean collects observational data,
schedules modeling codes for execution, manages data transfer, visualizes both observational and numerical results.
With all the information collected, Simulocean can also provide direct validation and verification for models,
and generate high quality technical reports.

.. _Simulocean: http://simulocean.ngchc.org/



